{
  "stem": "26731.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Quite well.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once, wondered perhaps in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were very nice, and in fact, I can't complain, I got Christmas presents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had actually a Christmas tree at Christmas time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course I had friends and non-Jewish friends and relatives who went to Christmas parties.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we occasionally went to church.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I found it very interesting, you could watch the organist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And while there was no cantor, there was singing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I actually enjoyed going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once in awhile.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Occasionally at Christmas, very nice, even now I like to go to Christmas service.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the sermon I don't recall too much, but I enjoy a sermon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A good sermon any denomination, even now I enjoy it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember the big church was quite-- people singing-- something different, but of course the organist really fascinated me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They have an organ in the liberal Synagogue too but you couldn't see it, but I could stand right next to organist and watch him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was seeing the number of songs that posted, you see, and everybody knew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was quite interesting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she wasn't religious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But she went to church occasionally, but [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] she probably would have converted, but my father said he didn't want it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You were raised, born Lutheran.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't want you to change.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually in Germany, you have to have a civil ceremony.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That is what counts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Legal is civil.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But afterwords you can go to religious ceremony, but you have to have a civil ceremony.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but at that time my father was the head of the family, he presented the family, therefore the children were to be raised Jewish.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's how it was done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember what happened, were several physicians present.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
